name: My Secret Garden - Seamless
description:
An image made to increase in beauty as your vision decreases from perfection, this image can be tiled with no obvious edge of each tile, making it excellent for computer backgrounds of all monitor resolutions, sizes, and shapes that give you the option to tile the background image.

"Let me show you my secret garden,
  where I grow my roses.
We have peas and green beans,
  and a little pond with minnows too.
It stretches on for what seems like forever,
   but I like this spot, right here with you."

Was inspired by Queer Platonic Relationship love with a Caretaker
